paragraphs.title: OrgOrders_NoMktVisitBefore_Updated
paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT orderDate
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT orderId) AS sdOrders
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN orderChannel = 'Direct' THEN orderId ELSE NULL END) AS directOrders
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN orderChannel = 'Direct' THEN guid ELSE NULL END) AS directOrdUsers
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN orderChannel = 'Direct' AND mktVisits7DaysBeforeOrd = 0 THEN guid ELSE NULL END) AS directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit7DaysBefore
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN orderChannel = 'Direct' AND mktVisits15DaysBeforeOrd = 0 THEN guid ELSE NULL END) AS directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit15DaysBefore
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN orderChannel = 'Direct' AND mktVisits30DaysBeforeOrd = 0 THEN guid ELSE NULL END) AS directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit30DaysBefore
FROM(
    SELECT guid
            ,orderId
            ,orderChannel
            ,orderDate
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 7 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS totVisits7DaysBeforeOrd
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel NOT IN ('Direct','Notification','Newsletter','SEO') AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 7 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS mktVisits7DaysBeforeOrd
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel = 'Direct' AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 7 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS directVisits7DaysBeforeOrd
            
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 15 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS totVisits15DaysBeforeOrd
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel NOT IN ('Direct','Notification','Newsletter','SEO') AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 15 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS mktVisits15DaysBeforeOrd
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel = 'Direct' AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 15 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS directVisits15DaysBeforeOrd
            
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 30 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS totVisits30DaysBeforeOrd
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel NOT IN ('Direct','Notification','Newsletter','SEO') AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 30 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS mktVisits30DaysBeforeOrd
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel = 'Direct' AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 30 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS directVisits30DaysBeforeOrd
    FROM `temp.mktDriven_OrgOrder_Data`
    
    GROUP BY guid
            ,orderId
            ,orderChannel
            ,orderDate
    )

GROUP BY orderDate
ORDER BY orderDate DESC
",1000)

paragraphs.title: OrgOrders_NoMktVisitBefore_WithWeek_Updated
paragraphs.text:
run("

SELECT date_add('2022-01-03',cast(datediff(to_date(
          orderDate
        ),'2022-01-03')/7 as int)*7) as week_start_date
        ,AVG(sdOrders) AS sdOrders
        ,AVG(directOrders) AS directOrders
        ,AVG(directOrdUsers) AS directOrdUsers
        ,AVG(directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit7DaysBefore) AS directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit7DaysBefore
        ,AVG(directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit15DaysBefore) AS directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit15DaysBefore
        ,AVG(directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit30DaysBefore) AS directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit30DaysBefore
FROM(
    SELECT orderDate
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT orderId) AS sdOrders
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN orderChannel = 'Direct' THEN orderId ELSE NULL END) AS directOrders
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN orderChannel = 'Direct' THEN guid ELSE NULL END) AS directOrdUsers
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN orderChannel = 'Direct' AND mktVisits7DaysBeforeOrd = 0 THEN guid ELSE NULL END) AS directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit7DaysBefore
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN orderChannel = 'Direct' AND mktVisits15DaysBeforeOrd = 0 THEN guid ELSE NULL END) AS directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit15DaysBefore
            ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN orderChannel = 'Direct' AND mktVisits30DaysBeforeOrd = 0 THEN guid ELSE NULL END) AS directOrdUsers_NoMktVisit30DaysBefore
    FROM(
        SELECT guid
                ,orderId
                ,orderChannel
                ,orderDate
                ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 7 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS totVisits7DaysBeforeOrd
                ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel <> 'Direct' AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 7 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS mktVisits7DaysBeforeOrd
                ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel = 'Direct' AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 7 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS directVisits7DaysBeforeOrd
                
                ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 15 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS totVisits15DaysBeforeOrd
                ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel <> 'Direct' AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 15 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS mktVisits15DaysBeforeOrd
                ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel = 'Direct' AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 15 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS directVisits15DaysBeforeOrd
                
                ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 30 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS totVisits30DaysBeforeOrd
                ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel <> 'Direct' AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 30 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS mktVisits30DaysBeforeOrd
                ,COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN visitChannel = 'Direct' AND DATEDIFF(orderDate,visitDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 30 THEN visitSessionId ELSE NULL END) AS directVisits30DaysBeforeOrd
        FROM `temp.mktDriven_OrgOrder_Data`
        
        GROUP BY guid
                ,orderId
                ,orderChannel
                ,orderDate
        )
    
    GROUP BY orderDate
    
    )

GROUP BY date_add('2022-01-03',cast(datediff(to_date(
          orderDate
        ),'2022-01-03')/7 as int)*7)
        
ORDER BY week_start_date DESC
",1000)
